## ğŸ§  Bonus Python Topics Covered Throughout the App:

| Skill                       | Where it's Covered                                              |
| --------------------------- | --------------------------------------------------------------- |
| **OOP Basics**              | Use in To-Do Manager or Expense Tracker (task/expense as class) |
